<h2>📊 Plan Usage Warning</h2>
<p>Hi there,</p>
<p>Your <strong>{{brandName}}</strong> account is approaching its plan limit for <strong>{{resource}}</strong>.</p>

<div class="{{#if isCritical}}danger-box{{else}}warning-box{{/if}}">
  <p>📈 Current usage: <strong>{{percentage}}%</strong> of your {{plan}} plan limit.</p>
  {{#if isCritical}}
  <p>🔴 You have reached or exceeded your limit. New {{resource}} creation may be blocked.</p>
  {{else}}
  <p>🟡 You are approaching your limit. Consider upgrading to avoid interruption.</p>
  {{/if}}
</div>

<p style="text-align:center;">
  <a href="{{upgradeLink}}" class="btn">Upgrade My Plan →</a>
</p>

<div class="divider"></div>
<p style="font-size:13px; color:#999;">You are on the <strong>{{plan}}</strong> plan. Upgrading gives you more capacity and access to advanced features.</p>
